# auto-status

## Context Profile

Load core workspace policy and SPEC headers/index only. Do not load full SPEC bodies, scenarios, canary, signatures, or learnings.

## Contract

1. Run `auto status` with all user arguments unchanged.
2. Group top-level and nested-module SPECs without crossing repository ownership boundaries.
3. Report draft, approved, implemented, completed, blocked, and unknown counts as observed.
4. Suggest the next eligible action without changing files or statuses.
